00:34:12.159 --> 00:34:15.870 align:middle line:84%
have a truly marvelous
diagnostic tool.

00:34:15.870 --> 00:34:18.670 align:middle line:84%
I've studied this
myself extensively.

00:34:18.670 --> 00:34:20.650 align:middle line:90%
It is an amazing science.

